---
title: Veggie Feijoada with Braised Kale, Bell Pepper and Sweet Potatoes
description: Feijoada is a classic Brazilian dish. Typically made with off-cuts of meat, this stew is traditionally simmered for hours, even days, to get a deep, rich flavour. Our veggie version is an homage to this Brazilian staple, ready in 30 minutes. Saude!
